release_note: Adds Artful Plus A new premium tier subscription option that includes: Habit Tracker Tab Daily Habit Tracker Ability to upload your own stickers Ability to create a custom color palette for seamless color coding across the app Drawing Mode for iPad Also recently released: Updates to the List Tab to allow organizing lists into folders. Adds premium cover options to the app. Updates the Choose Cover screen to use a Grid View. For tablet users add the ability to collapse the task and meal prep sections in the week view. Adds a home screen widget you may need to search to find the widget . Before submitting a review please report all issues to hello artfulagenda.com or through the app via Tech Support .
